BEGIN_TEXT

Convert the exponential equation \( Q = $a e^{$k t} \)
to the form \( Q = ab^{t} \) and enter the values of \(a\)
and \(b\) below.
$PAR
\( a = \) \{ ans_rule(10) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}
